### Create Report
POST http://localhost:3000/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "make": "ford",
  "model": "mustand",
  "year": 1982,
  "mileage": 50000,
  "lng": 45,
  "lat": 45,
  "price": 20000
}

### approve an existing request
PATCH http://localhost:3000/reports/7
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true
}

### get an estimate for an existing vehicle
GET http://localhost:3000/reports?make=ford&model=mustand&lng=45&lat=45&mileage=20000&year=1981